Alexandra Holden https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexandra_Holden 0 Alexandra Holden (born April 30, 1977) is an American actress. Her credits include films such as Drop Dead Gorgeous (1999) and The Hot Chick (2002), and recurring roles on Friends, Ally McBeal, Friday Night Lights, Franklin Bash, and Rizzoli Isles.
